===Etymology===
[[image:Passer montanus 2.jpg|thumb|{{ja-r|雀|すずめ}}]]
{{ja-kanjitab|すずめ|yomi=k}}
{{swp|ja:スズメ}}

{{rfe|ja}}

{{inh+|ja|ojp|-}}. The initial ''suzu'' is likely [[onomatopoetic]] of a sparrow's [[cry]], compare historical {{ja-r|しゅうしゅう}} or modern {{ja-r|ちゅうちゅう}}. The ''-me'' portion is likely the same as in {{ja-r|燕|つばめ|[[swallow]]}} and {{ja-r|鴎|かもめ|[[gull]]}}, interpreted as a synonym of {{ja-r|群れ|むれ|[[flock]]; [[herd]]}}.<ref>{{R:ja:SMKGGJT|p=517}}</ref>

